 Add Calculated Fields to Your Data Cloud Reports with Einstein Generative AI

You can use Einstein Report Formula Generation to create row-level and summary formulas. Describe a calculation in simple terms, and Einstein discovers the relevant data and suggests a formula.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions.
How: From Setup, enable Turn on Einstein, then edit a report and select Create Formula or Add Summary/Row-Level Formula.
In the formula builder, describe the calculation on the Einstein tab. Ask questions like "How many days did it take each opportunity to close?" If the formula looks good, click Insert Formula and Einstein fills in all the fields.
